succ_eq:

@[simp]
theorem succ_eq {n : ℕ} : succ_order.succ = fun a => if a < Fin.last n then a + 1 else a :=
  rfl
#align succ_eq succ_eq
succ_apply:
@[simp]
theorem succ_apply {n : ℕ} (a) : succ_order.succ a = if a < Fin.last n then a + 1 else a :=
  rfl
#align succ_apply succ_apply
pred_eq:
@[simp]
theorem pred_eq {n} : pred_order.pred = fun a : fin (n + 1) => if a = 0 then 0 else a - 1 :=
  rfl
#align pred_eq pred_eq
pred_apply:
@[simp]
theorem pred_apply {n : ℕ} (a : fin (n + 1)) : pred_order.pred a = if a = 0 then 0 else a - 1 :=
  rfl
#align pred_apply pred_apply
